         <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract:">Missionary.  President, Kobe College.  Papers include correspondence, memorabilia, photographs, clippings, awards and citations, and writings. Personal and professional correspondence includes letters from friends and colleagues in Japan, mostly relating to her work at Kobe College.
      </abstract>
